text: Linsdorf is a commune. It is in the Haut-Rhin department of eastern France. The mayor is Serge Gaisser. In 2014, 315 people lived in the commune. ==Population== ==Related pages== * Communes of the Haut-Rhin department ==References== *INSEE commune file ==Other websites== Category:Communes in Haut-Rhin
